snippet.title: High on Life Full Presentation | gamescom 2022 Xbox Booth
snippet.description:
We got a deeper dive into High on Life during the Xbox Booth showcase at gamescom with Mikey Spano (CCO and Art Director) and Matty Studivan (Executive Producer) from Squanch Games. Learn more about a run through a bounty. From various dialogue trees, to combat, and much more.

#xbox #gamescom #highonlife #gaming
